         <p>.mp4 and .mov files</p>
      </phystech>
      <prefercite id="aspace_ab28e331debe7681f6c0fcb66987ddce">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Music in the Black Church, Oral History of American Music, in the Music Library of Yale University.</p>
      </prefercite>
